settings.title:
Freshly baked
cookie dough
settings.content: We’ve been baking since 2014 and perfecting our recipes to bring you the best quality cookie dough & cookies, coffees, milkshakes and more. From kiosk to café, even straight to your door. With multiple locations in the UK & around the world, My Cookie Dough is the place to take time out of your busy day, bring family and friends together and indulge in the moment.

settings.content: Our sweet-toothed founders met at university and instantly connected over their passion for all things food. One evening, after trying to find a delicious dessert for movie night, they found themself stumped. There was nothing available that would satisfy their desire for something warm, sweet and indulgent.

settings.upper_content: They then began thinking up their dream dessert offering, and found they both had the knack and passion for creating delicious things, and so they set out to bless the world with something truly mouth-watering.
settings.bottom_content: Following weeks of testing, creating, tasting and perfecting like mad scientists they emerged, covered in crumbs and dusted with sugar, they had done it! The perfect cookie dough, which was nothing like the world had seen before. With a top secret recipe (hush hush!) and a one of a kind baking method, My Cookie Dough was born.

settings.content: Our cookie dough is freshly baked, soft, gooey and makes tastebuds squeal in delight. We’ve set out to play in the world of desserts, with the sole purple-wrapped mission of putting big smiles on faces. We bake our cookie dough with endless joy, so that your day can be just that little bit better.

After launching the UKs most successful cookie dough company My Cookie Dough was bombarded with requests for a baked cookie offering so customers could enjoy My Cookie Dough’s innovative and indulgent flavours anywhere at any time.

settings.upper_content: So, we took our original secret cookie dough recipe and developed it to make the best tasting baked cookies on the market, alongside developing our brand new vegan dough!
settings.bottom_content: My Cookies are the to go cookie brand for freshly baked cookies made with high quality ingredients that delivers on indulgence time and time again. Our revolving menu is based on seasonal flavours and reflect current trends and latest pastry techniques meaning that you will always have something new to try.

settings.content: Our cookies will never be bland and boring, you’ll always have something new and innovative to try. Want a flavour? Just request it. Drop us a line on Instagram or TikTok.

settings.content-sub-heading: Soft on the inside, crispy on the outside…
settings.content: Our Cookie Dough is made with the finest quality ingredients, a special recipe invented by our founders who know their food science! Although you need to bake the Cookie Dough, it always remains soft on the inside and crispy on the outside. They’re not Cookies, so get your spoons ready to indulge in the ultimate Cookie Dough treat 🥄🥄🥄
settings.download-pack-title: HERE ARE THE INSTRUCTIONAL LEAFLETS FOR OUR BIY PACKS:
settings.baking-tips: Tips for baking MyCookieDough like a pro:

settings.tip-content: Make sure you use baking paper when cooking
Ensure your oven is completely preheated before beginning to bake
It is a good idea to chill your baking tray before baking - your cookie dough should also be chilled

Once the cookie dough is slightly golden brown (usually after 8-9 minutes), remove it from the oven. You can use a large spatula to push on the 4 sides to prevent it expanding too much, and to help it keep its ‘square shape’.
Gently (very gently) wriggle the spatula completely under the cookie dough, before transferring to a plate to decorate & EAT!

settings.heading: My Cookie Dough Around The World
settings.left_content: Since opening our first store in the UK, we have expanded to several countries around the world, and we are looking forward to adding more countries and territories to our ever-growing portfolio next year.
settings.right_content:
Although we are growing fast, we will always strive to fulfil our mission, which is to serve moments of pure joy in everyone’s day. Our products generate a feeling of great pleasure, and our service helps to spread the happiness. We want to change people’s day and put a smile on their face, which we believe is something extremely special.

We want to spread this joy & happiness to all corners of the Earth, in a way that is ethically good, socially responsible & sustainable to the world around us.
